dc_title_s: Huebinger’s map and guide for Blue Grass Road: Council Bluffs, Burlington Ft. Madison, Muscatine, 1912
dc_description_s: Huebinger’s map and guide for Blue Grass Road: a model dirt road through the famous Blue Grass Belt of Iowa--Title cover. Descriptive essays of towns: Omaha -- Glenwood -- Malvern -- Hastings -- Emerson -- Red Oak -- Stanton -- Villisca -- Nodaway -- Corning -- Kent -- Creston -- Afton -- Russell -- Melrose -- Albia -- Ottumwa -- Fairfield -- Birmingham -- Burlington -- Denmark -- Fort Madison. Index, p. 48.; 1 atlas (134 p.): ill., maps, ports.; 13 x 20 cm. Material in the public domain. No restrictions on use. State Historical Society of Iowa (Iowa City) State Historical Society of Iowa (Des Moines)
